Summary: 4 lights spectating from each other and going round and round and coming back together making one circle
trends: There have been 4 other sightings in Flushing

divs: Sighting DetailsI have just got off the bus when something caught my attention, and so I looked up and I saw 4 lights ontop of my block going round and round and then after a few seconds, the four circles would come together and form one big circle and this process was repeated. I didn't know what to do so I just went home and I went back outside to check after 10 minutes and it was still there and as of right now, I'm not sure if it is or not.
